Project: Ungoverned Django App

Key models:
- Order (status: pending, building, completed, shipped, cancelled)
- ProductBuild
- ProductComponent
- StockMovement
- OrderItem

Key workflow:
Orders → Start Build → Vendetta BOM page → Build This Product

Build process:
- ProductBuild created
- StockMovement entries created (BUILD_CONSUME)
- Order status changes pending → building

